title: Toolbearer
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Your familiar can carry a set of tools of up to light Bulk. 

So long as your familiar is adjacent to you, you can draw and replace the tools as part of the action that uses them as if you were wearing them. 

Your familiar must have the [[Manual Dexterity]] ability to select this.